{"word":"G2548 - κἀκεῖνος - kakeînos - kak-i'-nos - And him","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κἀκεῖνος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kakeînos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kak-i'-nos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">And him</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"அவைகள், அவர்கள் - சுருக்கம்"},{"paragraph":"and he, he also"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2532 - καί - kaí - kahee/2532\">G2532</a> and <a href=\"#/G1565 - ἐκεῖνος - ekeînos - ek-i'-nos/1565\">G1565</a>; <i>likewise that</i> (or <i>those</i>): - and him (other, them), even he, him also, them (also), (and) they.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}